room_title: Escape room "Mission Escapossible" by Exitology Escape Room in Houston
room_description:
A malicious warlord named Ares has built an army intent to take over the world. Intelligence has reached our agency of a weapon more destructive than we have ever seen. Our top agent was sent undercover behind enemy lines to gather information on this weapon of mass destruction, but we have lost contact with our agent while he was deep in enemy territory.
Your mission is to infiltrate the enemy base by pretending to be arrested. Find information of the weapon before it is launched. You are our only hope.
